/* Loop Code */
// Volume Adjusted Weighted Moving Average
const Length = 120
const startingWeight = 1

let candle = record.current // Create everything from candles data

let volume = getElement('volumes', candle) // Get volume
let totalVolume = volume.buy + volume.sell // Candles Volumes split the volume received from the exchange

let src = (candle.max + candle.min + candle.close) / 3  // use HLC3 data as source

variable.volArr.push(totalVolume)
variable.sourceArr.push(src)

let output = 0
const last = Length - 1
let vol = 0
let sum = 0


if (variable.volArr.length > Length) {
    variable.volArr.splice(0, 1)     // keep array at maximum length
    variable.sourceArr.splice(0, 1)

    for (i = 0; i < Length; i++) {
        let source = variable.sourceArr.at(-i - 1)
        let v = variable.volArr.at(-i - 1)

        let m = last - i + startingWeight
        v *= m
        vol += v
        sum += source * v

        output = sum / vol
    }
}

variable.value = output

// T3 Moving Average
const pLength = 20
const t3hot = 1

let candle = record.current // Create everything from candles data
let alpha = t3hot
let source = candle.close


//Calculate T3
let c1 = -alpha * alpha * alpha
let c2 = 3 * alpha * alpha + 3 * alpha * alpha * alpha
let c3 = -6 * alpha * alpha - 3 * alpha - 3 * alpha * alpha * alpha
let c4 = 1 + 3 * alpha + alpha * alpha * alpha + 3 * alpha * alpha

let alpha1 = 2.0 / (2.0 + (pLength - 1.0) / 2.0)

let t30 = source, t31 = source
let t32 = source, t33 = source
let t34 = source, t35 = source

t30 = variable.t30prev + alpha1 * (source - variable.t30prev)
t31 = variable.t31prev + alpha1 * (t30 - variable.t31prev)
t32 = variable.t32prev + alpha1 * (t31 - variable.t32prev)
t33 = variable.t33prev + alpha1 * (t32 - variable.t33prev)
t34 = variable.t34prev + alpha1 * (t33 - variable.t34prev)
t35 = variable.t35prev + alpha1 * (t34 - variable.t35prev)
let T3_1 = c1 * t35 + c2 * t34 + c3 * t33 + c4 * t32



////////////////////////////////
variable.value = T3_1        // final output value



// save values for next iteration
variable.t30prev = t30
variable.t31prev = t31
variable.t32prev = t32
variable.t33prev = t33
variable.t34prev = t34
variable.t35prev = t35

variable.M5arr = []

variable.value = 0

/* Loop Code */
// Gann Swing Signals by quantum8
const periods = 3

const candle = record.current // Create everything from candles data
variable.highs.push(candle.max)
variable.lows.push(candle.min)

let sma1 = 0
let sma2 = 0
let iff_1 = 0
let hld = 0
let hlv = variable.holdVal1

if (variable.highs.length > periods) {
    variable.highs.splice(0, 1)
    variable.lows.splice(0, 1)

    sma1 = variable.highs.reduce((a, b) => (a + b)) / variable.highs.length
    sma2 = variable.lows.reduce((a, b) => (a + b)) / variable.lows.length

    iff_1 = candle.close < variable.sma2prev ? -1 : 0
    hld = candle.close > variable.sma1prev ? 1 : iff_1

    // approximate the valuewhen() function
    if (hld != 0) {
        variable.holdVal1 = variable.holdVal
        variable.holdVal = hld
        hlv = variable.holdVal1     // update to new value

        // more logic here to hold the values longer, only if hlv changes?
        if (variable.dnTrendPrev && variable.upTrend) {
            variable.upPlot = candle.min * 0.98
        }
        if (variable.upTrendPrev && variable.dnTrend) {
            variable.dnPlot = candle.max * 1.02
        }
    }
}


let hi = hlv == -1 ? sma1 : NaN
let lo = hlv == 1 ? sma2 : NaN

let BHcloseAbove = candle.close > hi && variable.closePrev < hi ? 1 : 0
let BHcloseBelow = candle.close < lo && variable.closePrev > lo ? -1 : 0

variable.bgCol = (BHcloseAbove == 1) ? 1 : (BHcloseBelow == -1) ? -1 : 0

variable.dnTrendPrev = variable.dnTrend
variable.upTrendPrev = variable.upTrend
variable.dnTrend = isFinite(hi) ? true : false
variable.upTrend = isFinite(lo) ? true : false


// save for next iteration
variable.sma1prev = sma1
variable.sma2prev = sma2
variable.closePrev = candle.close
